1. [rejected] use Observer pattern for state changes (register, flags, memory)
2. [done] make a single common function for state changes:
    e.g. __view.update(state) can be have common implementation like:
                ViewState state = {
                    .machine_code = cmd->get_machine_code(),
                    .address = cmd->get_address(),
                };
                __view.update(state);
        - this can then be called for both handle_enter(), handle_backspace(), etc.

3. [x] backspace and enter are becoming complicated too complicated due to machine code, address and source code being stored on enter press - ignore not doing
